{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother and brother--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, where the-- the count's, the baron's apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just said, you know, nobody in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were only a few people left, mostly some older people and a couple of young women with children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just said, I was in the-- I was in the army, and I was just been you know, discharged.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or I gave them some reason that were-- that they wouldn't get suspicious.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then it was still dangerous, because if all-- because that was the days before the Russians attacked the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was-- the street-- the city was crowded you know, with German military personnel of all stripes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, there was everybody-- the SS, you know, army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they organized people out of-- they organized a resistance group of people that were senior citizens-- 60 years and older, 75 years old-- gave them rifles, honestly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Put on those air raid warden helmets and expect them to take positions on street corners, and-- honesty, and hold-- and hold off the Russians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, that's total nonsense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was-- but it was not a good time for me to go out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because being a young person, it looked like somebody saw me, they wouldn't-- wouldn't even care if I was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would care-- they would more think I'm an AWOL German soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were looking for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they strung them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They caught people like this, soldiers like this, that had gone AWOL.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They strung them up on lampposts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw them hanging.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was not a good idea to go out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I stayed in the-- you know, and it was difficult, because I had hardly anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
